@startuml Sequence_Checkin
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2

title **BIỂU ĐỒ TUẦN TỰ - CHECK-IN & CẬP NHẬT STREAK**

actor "Người dùng" as User #LightGreen
participant "Dashboard\n(/dashboard)" as Dashboard #E3F2FD
participant "Check-in Page\n(/checkin)" as CheckinPage #FFF3E0
participant "API Client\n(Axios)" as API #FCE4EC
participant "DecisionController" as Controller #E8F5E9
participant "DecisionService" as DecService #C8E6C9
participant "StreakService" as StreakService #FFF9C4
database "MongoDB" as DB #F3E5F5

== Bước 1: Xem nhiệm vụ hôm nay ==

User -> Dashboard : Truy cập /dashboard
activate Dashboard

Dashboard -> API : GET /api/decisions/today
activate API
API -> DB : Decision.find({\n  userId,\n  status: "pending",\n  expiresAt: {$gt: now}\n}).populate('choiceId')
activate DB
DB --> API : pendingDecisions[]
deactivate DB
API --> Dashboard : pendingDecisions[]
deactivate API

Dashboard --> User : Hiển thị card "Nhiệm vụ hôm nay"\n🍜 Bún bò Huế\n⏰ Còn 18h để check-in\n[📸 Check-in ngay]
deactivate Dashboard

== Bước 2: Mở trang Check-in ==

User -> Dashboard : Nhấn "Check-in ngay"
activate Dashboard
Dashboard -> CheckinPage : navigate('/checkin?id=...')
deactivate Dashboard
activate CheckinPage

CheckinPage --> User : Form check-in:\n- Nhiệm vụ: Bún bò Huế\n- ⏰ Còn 18h\n- [📷 Upload ảnh]\n- Đánh giá: ☆☆☆☆☆\n- Caption (tùy chọn)

== Bước 3: Điền form check-in ==

User -> CheckinPage : 1. Chọn/chụp ảnh
CheckinPage -> CheckinPage : Preview ảnh\nValidate: JPEG/PNG, < 5MB

User -> CheckinPage : 2. Đánh giá ⭐⭐⭐⭐☆ (4 sao)
User -> CheckinPage : 3. Viết caption:\n"Tô bún bò ngon lắm!"

== Bước 4: Gửi check-in ==

User -> CheckinPage : Nhấn "Hoàn thành Check-in"
activate CheckinPage

CheckinPage -> CheckinPage : Validate:\n- Ảnh đã chọn? ✅\n- Rating đã chọn? ✅

CheckinPage -> API : POST /api/decisions/:id/checkin\nContent-Type: multipart/form-data\n{image: File, rating: 4,\ncaption: "Tô bún bò ngon lắm!"}
activate API

API -> Controller : checkin(req, res)
activate Controller

Controller -> DecService : checkin(decisionId,\nimage, caption, rating)
activate DecService

== Bước 5: Xử lý server ==

DecService -> DB : Decision.findById(decisionId)
activate DB
DB --> DecService : decision
deactivate DB

DecService -> DecService : Kiểm tra:\n- decision.status == "pending"? ✅\n- decision.expiresAt > now? ✅\n- decision.userId == req.user? ✅

DecService -> DecService : Lưu file ảnh\n(local storage /uploads)

DecService -> DB : Decision.findByIdAndUpdate(id, {\n  status: "completed",\n  checkin: {\n    imageUrl: "/uploads/xxx.jpg",\n    caption: "Tô bún bò ngon lắm!",\n    rating: 4,\n    completedAt: new Date()\n  }\n})
activate DB
DB --> DecService : updated decision
deactivate DB

DecService -> DB : Choice.findByIdAndUpdate(\n  choiceId,\n  {$inc: {timesCompleted: 1}}\n)
activate DB
DB --> DecService : updated choice
deactivate DB

== Bước 6: Cập nhật Streak ==

DecService -> StreakService : incrementStreak(userId)
activate StreakService

StreakService -> DB : UserStreak.findOne({userId})
activate DB
DB --> StreakService : streak (hoặc null)
deactivate DB

alt Chưa có streak record
  StreakService -> DB : UserStreak.create({\n  userId,\n  currentStreak: 1,\n  longestStreak: 1,\n  totalCheckins: 1,\n  lastCheckinDate: today,\n  streakStartDate: today,\n  level: 1\n})
  activate DB
  DB --> StreakService : new streak
  deactivate DB
else Đã check-in hôm nay
  StreakService -> StreakService : totalCheckins++\nKhông thay đổi streak
else Ngày liên tiếp (yesterday)
  StreakService -> StreakService : currentStreak++\ntotalCheckins++\nlastCheckinDate = today
  StreakService -> StreakService : if currentStreak > longestStreak:\n  longestStreak = currentStreak
else Bị gián đoạn (> 1 ngày)
  StreakService -> StreakService : currentStreak = 1\ntotalCheckins++\nstreakStartDate = today\nlastCheckinDate = today
end

== Bước 7: Tính Level ==

StreakService -> StreakService : calculateLevel(currentStreak):\n  0-2   → Level 1 (Newcomer 🌱)\n  3-6   → Level 2 (Starter ⭐)\n  7-13  → Level 3 (Decisive 🔥)\n  14-29 → Level 4 (Committed 💪)\n  30-59 → Level 5 (Master 👑)\n  60-99 → Level 6 (Legend 💎)\n  100+  → Level 7 (Unstoppable 🏆)

== Bước 8: Kiểm tra Badge ==

StreakService -> StreakService : checkBadges():

group Kiểm tra từng badge
  StreakService -> StreakService : first_spin?\n  totalDecisions >= 1 → ✅ Đã có
  StreakService -> StreakService : perfect_week?\n  currentStreak >= 7 → ✅ Đã có
  StreakService -> DB : Đếm check-in theo\ncategory "do-an"
  activate DB
  DB --> StreakService : count = 8
  deactivate DB
  StreakService -> StreakService : foodie?\n  count >= 10 → ❌ Chưa đạt
  StreakService -> DB : Đếm số category\nđã check-in
  activate DB
  DB --> StreakService : distinctCategories = 3
  deactivate DB
  StreakService -> StreakService : explorer?\n  count >= 5 → ❌ Chưa đạt
end

StreakService -> DB : UserStreak.findByIdAndUpdate({\n  currentStreak, longestStreak,\n  totalCheckins, level,\n  lastCheckinDate, badges\n})
activate DB
DB --> StreakService : updated streak
deactivate DB

StreakService --> DecService : {streak, newBadges: []}
deactivate StreakService

DecService --> Controller : {decision, streak}
deactivate DecService

Controller --> API : 200 OK\n{success: true, data: {\n  decision: {..., status: "completed"},\n  streak: {\n    currentStreak: 13,\n    level: 3,\n    newBadges: []\n  }\n}}
deactivate Controller

API --> CheckinPage : Response
deactivate API

== Bước 9: Hiển thị kết quả ==

CheckinPage -> CheckinPage : Animation thành công 🎉\nConfetti + success message

CheckinPage --> User : "Check-in thành công!\n🔥 Streak: 13 ngày\n⭐ Level 3 - Decisive"
deactivate CheckinPage

User -> Dashboard : Quay về Dashboard
activate Dashboard
Dashboard --> User : Cập nhật streak mới\nvà lịch sử
deactivate Dashboard

@enduml
